### ProServe X — API & Page Test Requests

### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### PUBLIC PAGES
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Homepage
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Search Providers
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/

### Search with query
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/?q=john&category=electrician&city=New+York

### All Providers
GET {{baseUrl}}/providers/

### Providers by Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/providers/category/electrician/

### Provider Detail (replace :id with actual pk)
GET {{baseUrl}}/providers/1/

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### AUTHENTICATION
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Login Page
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/login/

### Register Page
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/register/

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### PROTECTED PAGES (requires login/session)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Dashboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/dashboard/

### My Bookings
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/

### Edit Provider Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/providers/edit/

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### ADMIN
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Admin Panel
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### STATIC FILES
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### CSS
GET {{baseUrl}}/static/css/style.css

### JS
GET {{baseUrl}}/static/js/main.js
